Carnage/ Dinobot

(Carnage: Sorry that I haven't posted today so far, had to go to a Birthday 
Party. Yuck!)

* Carnage continued to walk towards the action on the other side of the 
island, she sighed as she was sprayed by the salty water that Cyber Claw 
shook off. It had been such a long time since she had been around many bots, 
she wasn't sure if she could handel it anylonger. She didn't like crowds, 
just as no assassin did.
Carnage sighed again, she was now only 100 clicks from the action.
Soon she would have to battle just to get her friend to be accepted as a 
Maximal in their group, battle against the very race that had b=made her 
what she was today...a cold blooded killer!*

************************ *************************** *************

* Dinobot roared as he saw Megatron escaping from his weapon fire, what a 
coward he had become!
He snarled in rage but then smiled to himself as his systems located the 
Predacon as he moved towards the bridge through a ventilation shaft, he 
wouldn't make it there alive!
Dinobot began to walk around the battle about him, his head always tilted 
towards the ventilation shaft in which his target traveled within. He 
growled as he aimed his rifle at the shaft and let a mirage of charges go at 
the location of the signature he detected, he wasn't about to let Megatron 
go...not now!*
